Package wahoot.db.models

Class Classroom

java.lang.Object
wahoot.db.models.Classroom
@Entity public class Classroom extends Object
Represents a classroom entity in the application. Classrooms are unique entities that contain quizzes, are assigned a teacher, and have enrolled students.
